Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, there's something I've been wondering about for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's inside those hair buns of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Deko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume it's morning stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.03,Old,,0,0,0,,{\pos(860,365)\frz12\blur0.6}This
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}did{\i0} use morning stars as her hammer in her battle with Forest Summer a while back, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Their usual content really {\i1}is{\i0} a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A real mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't look like all there's inside is hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering about it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what {\i1}is{\i0} inside them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is inside those buns on your hair-ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Will not knowing it accelerate your death?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to know that badly, I might just entrust you with my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us, Deko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I decline now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, lower your head to the floor and beg as if you're trying to avert your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know it {\i1}that{\i0} badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's something stupid anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Show it to those who want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say "show me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, show us then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really all you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}All right, pay close attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So there were sweets inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sweet buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The basic ingredient of my buns is candy of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They work as snacks and increase my attack stats as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An exemplary case of hitting two birds with one stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprise it hurts when you hit me with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Dekomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You combined food supplies with attack power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you saying that makes is worth being your servant, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd been putting cookies in there a while ago,\Nbut that didn't turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So after that I've been using candy of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,600,0,,Cookies aren't that sturdy, are they?
